description:
Hi guys, I just created some art for fun.
No usecase. 
Just some little pictures which I created.
If you like it, buy one.

In this collection it's about european sights / cities and places. 
All made with the help of ai in some kind of synthwave style.

Just 20 NFTs:
Athens, Barcelona, Berlin, Hamburg, Istanbul, London, Malmo, Paris, Rome, Stonehenge

(From every "place" there are 2 different pictures)
name: art by aiy - collection 1 [european sights: synthwave style]
